properties.areaDesc: Munising to Grand Marais MI; Grand Marais to Whitefish Point MI; Marquette to Munising MI
properties.headline: Gale Watch issued January 3 at 3:30PM EST until January 6 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the Small Craft Advisory, waves 3 to 5 feet
occurring. For the Gale Watch, west winds 15 to 25 kt with
gusts up to 35 kt and waves 6 to 11 feet possible.

* WHERE...Marquette to Munising MI, Munising to Grand Marais MI
and Grand Marais to Whitefish Point MI.

* WHEN...For the Small Craft Advisory, until 4 PM EST this
afternoon. For the Gale Watch, from Sunday evening through
Monday morning.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid possible
hazardous conditions.  Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter
course, and/or secure the vessel for severe wind and waves.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON... ...GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM SUNDAY EVENING THROUGH MONDAY MORNING
